	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Create a new Meeting</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click New Task</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Enter these compulsory fields; date, time and description</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Reminders will be send to you as a memo</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Specify a recurrence (daily, weekly or monthly)</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">If set to Private, the details of the meeting cannot be seen by other users</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">6.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Compulsory attendees have no option to respond</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">7.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Optional attendees have an Accept/Reject button</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">8.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select the resource(s) you need (user defined) for this meeting. Use the '>>' button to bring them into the Selected box.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">9.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Automatically notify the meeting participants via memo/email</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">10.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Finally, click Submit. The new event will check for conflicts in your calendar and availability of  the resource(s)</td>
